entry.summary: Kathyleen Beveridge Born in Vietnam, moved to San Diego in 2004 Received her bachelors degree in Santa Clara bay area, then received a degree at USC Lives by a mission statement, says my mission in life is to not merely survive, but to thrive and to do so with passion… Career First job was an investment banker at Wells Fargo, was a stock broker, mutual funds Went back to university and switch careers after at High Tech Took six months off in San Diego, learned how to surf Switched again, went to Qualcomm, then left Companies HP Inc: Create technology that makes life better for everyone, everywhere Qualcomm: Inventing the tech the world loves Thermo Fisher Scientific: Enable our customers to make the world healthier, cleaner, and safer Every company wants to code for the betterment of life and society Thermo Fisher products that they make, make a massive impact Her title is senior director for marketing and sales
